00:17:40.400 --> 00:17:41.039
aking panginoon,

00:17:41.759 --> 00:17:43.640
Ibabalik ko ang Divine Sword.

00:17:44.319 --> 00:17:46.000
Pinag-isipan mo na ba ito?

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:47.640
Kahit na ano,

00:17:48.319 --> 00:17:48.880
gagawin ko

00:17:49.200 --> 00:17:50.039
gampanan ang gawain.

00:17:56.160 --> 00:17:58.080
(Sanqing Art)

00:18:32.559 --> 00:18:34.680
Kaya naparito ka para hanapin ang kamatayan ngayon?

00:18:35.240 --> 00:18:36.119
pumunta ako dito

00:18:36.640 --> 00:18:37.960
upang bawiin ang Banal na Espada,

00:18:38.519 --> 00:18:39.880
at para ipaghiganti si Xiaoying!

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.440
Kung hindi mo siya mahal,

00:18:42.759 --> 00:18:44.000
dapat lumayo ka sa kanya.

00:18:44.559 --> 00:18:45.240
ngayon,

00:18:45.920 --> 00:18:48.799
Pagbabayaran kita sa ginawa mo.

00:18:49.880 --> 00:18:50.920
Ikaw?

00:18:51.440 --> 00:18:52.440
Oo, ako.

00:19:14.960 --> 00:19:17.119
Mukhang mamamatay ka dito ngayon.

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:20.200
Ipapakuha ko kay Bai Xiaoying
ang bangkay mo.

00:19:23.720 --> 00:19:25.279
Huwag mong sabihin ang pangalan niya.

00:19:30.079 --> 00:19:31.799
Naghanda ka.

00:21:48.880 --> 00:21:50.480
Bakit nandito ang Divine Sword?

00:22:01.920 --> 00:22:02.680
Master!

00:22:05.440 --> 00:22:06.000
Tumigil ka!

00:22:06.000 --> 00:22:06.848
(Yunxiu Pavilion)

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:09.799
kailangan ko ng pumasok.

00:22:09.880 --> 00:22:11.240
Wala nang makikita si Master ngayon.

00:22:11.960 --> 00:22:12.519
(Maghintay.)

00:22:13.559 --> 00:22:15.720
(Hindi ko pa nakita ang Yunxiu Pavilion
na ganito kahigpit na binabantayan.)

00:22:16.599 --> 00:22:17.680
(May sira.)

00:22:18.119 --> 00:22:18.960
Dapat ko siyang makita.

00:22:19.839 --> 00:22:20.240
Tumigil ka!

00:22:22.759 --> 00:22:23.400
ano ngayon?

00:22:23.759 --> 00:22:24.599
Panloob na alitan?

00:22:26.839 --> 00:22:27.680
Yongning,

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:30.160
Alam kong binawi ni Master
ang Divine Sword para sa akin.

00:22:31.279 --> 00:22:33.119
Ngunit ang Yunxiu Pavilion
ay mahigpit na binabantayan,

00:22:33.519 --> 00:22:34.920
dapat may nangyari.

00:22:35.759 --> 00:22:37.319
Bilang matalik niyang kaibigan,

00:22:37.319 --> 00:22:38.599
dapat alam mo ang nangyari.

00:22:39.279 --> 00:22:40.519
Pakisabi sa akin.

00:22:44.759 --> 00:22:45.559
Sumama ka sa akin.

00:23:01.240 --> 00:23:02.359
Alam niyang malalaman mo ito,

00:23:03.839 --> 00:23:05.680
ngunit nais na maantala hangga't maaari.

00:23:06.559 --> 00:23:08.400
Ayaw niyang
nakikita mo siyang ganito.

00:23:26.119 --> 00:23:27.039
Bakit?

00:23:29.440 --> 00:23:30.680
Bakit siya magiging ganito?

00:23:32.279 --> 00:23:33.160
para sayo,

00:23:33.960 --> 00:23:35.680
upang talunin si Ye Chenyuan,

00:23:36.240 --> 00:23:38.079
nakipagsapalaran siya sa paggamit ng ipinagbabawal na pamamaraan

00:23:38.839 --> 00:23:40.799
at pumuntang mag-isa para bawiin ang espada.

00:23:42.119 --> 00:23:43.720
Isang pagpapala ang mawalan ng isang braso.

00:23:44.880 --> 00:23:47.759
Ngayon ang kanyang walang kamatayang kamalayan ay kumukupas
at ang kanyang espirituwal na kapangyarihan ay naglalaho.

00:23:48.960 --> 00:23:50.559
Kahit si Xiyuan ay walang magawa.

00:23:52.119 --> 00:23:54.480
Malamang na mananatili siyang ganito magpakailanman.

00:23:57.480 --> 00:23:58.119
Hindi pwede.

00:23:59.519 --> 00:24:00.200
Hindi pwede.

00:24:07.519 --> 00:24:08.160
Master.

00:24:10.559 --> 00:24:11.319
Master.

00:24:21.440 --> 00:24:22.400
Master.

00:24:29.799 --> 00:24:30.240
Hindi!

00:24:31.559 --> 00:24:32.000
Hindi!

00:24:36.680 --> 00:24:38.160
Tama si Wanyan.

00:24:42.279 --> 00:24:45.279
Patuloy akong nagdulot ng gulo kay Master.

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:50.279
Kasalanan ko lahat.

00:24:56.559 --> 00:24:57.480
Master.

00:24:57.720 --> 00:24:58.720
pasensya na po.

00:24:59.680 --> 00:25:01.160
Paumanhin, Guro.

00:25:02.119 --> 00:25:04.079
Kasalanan ko lahat.

00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:22.079
Ye Chenyuan.

00:25:24.680 --> 00:25:26.240
Ye Chenyuan.

00:25:32.559 --> 00:25:33.960
Ye Chenyuan.

00:25:35.799 --> 00:25:37.240
Mula ngayon,

00:25:39.119 --> 00:25:41.640
Ako ang magiging sinumpaang kalaban mo!

00:25:43.359 --> 00:25:45.960
Hinding hindi kita bibitawan!

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:58.279
Ako si Bai Xiaoying,
Sword Master of Nine Heavens.

00:25:58.640 --> 00:26:00.880
Pumunta ako dito
para maghiganti kay Ye Chenyuan.

00:26:01.720 --> 00:26:03.039
Kung hindi siya lalabas,

00:26:03.920 --> 00:26:04.720
pagkatapos

00:26:05.359 --> 00:26:07.440
buburahin ko kayong lahat!

00:26:35.599 --> 00:26:36.480
Ye Chenyuan.

00:26:38.559 --> 00:26:38.920
Hindi.

00:26:40.440 --> 00:26:41.359
Panggabing Diyosa.

00:26:43.599 --> 00:26:44.759
Nagkita ulit tayo.

00:26:46.680 --> 00:26:48.039
Tulad ng iyong panginoon,

00:26:49.000 --> 00:26:50.599
dumating nang hindi imbitado.

00:26:52.680 --> 00:26:54.640
Nakakatuwa kayong mga tao sa Nine Heavens.

00:26:54.759 --> 00:26:56.079
Huwag mong sabihin ang kanyang pangalan.

00:26:59.720 --> 00:27:00.799
Sa loob ng sampung taon,

00:27:02.599 --> 00:27:05.440
Ilang beses ko nang naisip
kung paano ko papatayin ang Night Deity.

00:27:07.839 --> 00:27:09.720
Ngunit hindi ko inaasahan kung kailan dumating ang araw,

00:27:11.240 --> 00:27:12.599
Malungkot sana ako.

00:27:18.759 --> 00:27:19.559
Ye Chenyuan.

00:27:21.319 --> 00:27:23.079
Wala akong pakialam kung anong dahilan mo.

00:27:24.759 --> 00:27:26.880
Pinutol namin ang relasyon

00:27:26.960 --> 00:27:28.039
dito!

00:27:30.079 --> 00:27:31.039
ngayon,

00:27:32.480 --> 00:27:34.720
Maghahanap ako ng hustisya para sa aking amo!

00:27:35.279 --> 00:27:36.519
nakikita ko.

00:27:37.880 --> 00:27:39.400
Kahit gaano pa kita pinahirapan,

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:41.799
nanatili kang binubuo.

00:27:42.920 --> 00:27:44.359
Ang lahat ng ito ay dahil sa iyong amo.

00:27:46.279 --> 00:27:48.680
Kamukha ni Yunya

00:27:49.799 --> 00:27:51.039
ay ang iyong tunay na kahinaan.

00:27:52.839 --> 00:27:53.839
Kaya ano?

00:27:55.079 --> 00:27:55.880
Perpekto.

00:27:56.480 --> 00:27:58.039
Ayusin na natin lahat ng sama ng loob natin

00:27:58.640 --> 00:27:59.640
sabay-sabay.

00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:01.200
ayos lang.

00:28:02.720 --> 00:28:03.400
ngayon,

00:28:04.400 --> 00:28:06.240
tapusin na natin ang lahat ng ito.

00:28:57.440 --> 00:28:58.359
Ye Chenyuan, ikaw...

